{"data":[{"date":"15:56 12/08","title":"Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/12/23/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1eeb Lazio, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng, anh v\u1eeba ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 12 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Cristiano-Ronaldo-muon-Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m. MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic, Man City, Barca, Real hay PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Lazio, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1eeb Lazio, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Cristiano-Ronaldo-muon-Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic--hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCR7 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia, anh mu\u1ed1n Juventus chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Milinkovic-Savic, b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Lazio y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chi\u1ec1u l\u00f2ng CR7 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi chi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ronaldol, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia. Ngo\u00e0i Milinkovic-Savic, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Marcelo </span>c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, song th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5399","checkdouble":"194317"},{"date":"14:54 12/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vs Mes Sungun Varzaghan 18h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/link-xem-thai-son-nam-vs-mes-sungun-varzaghan-futsal-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vs Mes Sungun Varzaghan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam vs Mes Sungun Varzaghan chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i Futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u00e1c CLB l\u00fac 18h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 12/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>LINK XEM TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnextin.vn%2Fvideos%2F2128474780760021%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden\" scrolling=\"no\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"100%\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> - Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh: H\u1ed3 V\u0103n \u00dd, Roberto Tobe, Nguy\u1ec5n Minh Tr\u00ed, T\u00f4n Th\u1ea5t Phi, Al-Tawail.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/anh4.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam t\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal ch\u00e2u \u00c1</h2>\r\nB\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bank of Beirut (Lebanon) d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-1 \u1edf hi\u1ec7p hai, Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 6-5 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nagoya Ocean - nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch futsal Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.\r\n<h2>HLV Miguel Rodrigo: 'T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam'</h2>\r\nThuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bank of Beirut (Lebanon) t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i futsal c\u00e1c CLB ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Miguel Rodrigo d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &quot;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 3-1. S\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nTh\u00e1i S\u01a1n Nam 6-5 Beirut\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/10/Thai-Son-Nam-FC-6-5-Bank-of-Beirut.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5398","checkdouble":"194313"},{"date":"15:59 12/08","title":"Danh th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/danh-thu-nhat-ban-se-doi-dau-tuyen-viet-nam-tai-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Campuchia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Keisuke Honda v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean CLB Melbourne Victory n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00f3i chung b\u1edfi l\u1ebd Keisuke Honda th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eeba \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB Melbourne City \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia Australia sau k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keisuke Honda l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Campuchia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keisuke Honda l\u00e0m gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Campuchia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/df.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Campuchia t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. \u1ea2nh: CNCC.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho CLB n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Melbourne Victory l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Australia. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau, ch\u00fang ta h\u00e3y bi\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u n\u00e0y gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi theo CNCC, Keisuke Honda \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV khi c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Melbourne Victory \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Honda kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Prak Sovannara \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Campuchia sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Leonardo Vitorino ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Keisuke Honda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp CLB Melbourne Victory, Honda t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Mexico trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Pachuca. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, anh v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, khi \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Keisuke Honda l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1eebng chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 CSKA Moscow v\u00e0 AC Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Honda t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Campuchia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 AFF Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Zing.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5397","checkdouble":"194319"},{"date":"14:39 12/08","title":"Real Madrid chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/25/real-madrid-chot-eriksen-thay-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Christian Eriksen trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Luka Modric t\u1edbi Inter Milan, theo The Sun Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Inter Milan</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i song v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid mua Christian Eriksen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid mua Christian Eriksen h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chi-75-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-mua-Christian-Eriksen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan li\u00ean h\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\" target=\"_blank\">Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng khai \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Marca, s\u1edf h\u1eefu Inter Milan v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric l\u00e0 b\u1edfi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu, sau nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Los Blancos anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nModric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Italia kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan, anh mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ivan Perisic. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u1ed1t Christian Eriksen thay Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Real Madrid c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Eriksen\" title=\"tien ve Eriksen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Christian-Eriksen-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Eriksen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Spurs, anh c\u00f3 nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 lu\u00f4n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid mua Christian Eriksen trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Luka Modric t\u1edbi Inter Milan, theo The Sun Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Tottenham \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh khi b\u1ecf qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n x\u00e2y SV\u0110 m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Eriksen v\u1edbi Tottenham c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Spurs ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Los Blancos s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5396","checkdouble":"194307"},{"date":"13:01 12/08","title":"Lopetegui: \"Bale \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng thay Ronaldo\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/lopetegui-bale-da-san-sang-toa-sang-thay-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng Bale v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Real Madrid sau khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chia tay s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bale kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u t\u1ea1i Real Madrid khi ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Bale v\u00e0 Benzema h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Bale v\u00e0 Benzema h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Lopetegui-dat-niem-tin-vao-Bale-va-Benzema-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Lopetegui \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Bale - Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3\u201d, Lopetegui chia s\u1ebb sau khi Bale ghi b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGareth Bale c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n gi\u1edd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Real \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i La Liga khi Benzema ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n sau 32 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Real. V\u00e0 Lopetegui c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00fap Benzema l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec Benzema. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u00fap \u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-real-madrid-31-ac-milan-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-194289.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 3-1 AC Milan (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-372-194278.html\">Real Madrid 3-1 AC Milan: M\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5395","checkdouble":"194308"},{"date":"15:10 12/08","title":"Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo ESPN \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele cho Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u euro ch\u1ec9 ghi c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n sau 19 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf La Liga, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Dembele. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft kinh ph\u00ed mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00eda Barca \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd\u00a0kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Arsenal b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele-180-194246.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Dembele</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a sau \u0111\u00f3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2018/19, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 PSG b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t Dembele l\u00ean t\u1edbi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Dembele cho PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda PSG, theo \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Dembele cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paul Pogba t\u1eeb M.U.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Ousmane Dembele cho PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo ESPN \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Dembele l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Barca, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Cavani, Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Dembele \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5394","checkdouble":"194312"},{"date":"16:21 12/08","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Gerard Pique chia tay s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/chinh-thuc-gerard-pique-chia-tay-su-nghiep-quoc-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, sau khi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Enrique.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPique t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, b\u1edfi scandal c\u1ee7a HLV julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0o n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T, sau khi c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c suy ngh\u0129 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Luis Enrique m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc&rdquo; &ndash; Pique cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi th\u0103m t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u1ea5p \u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung v\u1ec7 Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" title=\"Pique gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/chinh-thuc-gerard-pique-chia-tay-su-nghiep-quoc-te.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Trung v\u1ec7 Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 EURO. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cho Barcelona. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo; &ndash; Pique x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o B\u00f2 t\u00f3t, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 102 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, gi\u00e0nh World Cup 2010 t\u1ea1i Nam Phi v\u00e0 EURO 2 n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha-180-194300.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha-180-194300.html\">Sevilla t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u00ean v\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span><br>\r\nSevilla t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Andalusia tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Barcelona th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-194312.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-194312.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo ESPN \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-sevilla-vs-barca-3h-ngay-138-co-messi-la-co-tat-ca-180-194294.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Sevilla vs Barca (3h ng\u00e0y 13/8): C\u00f3 Messi l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nBarcelona m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. Nh\u01b0ng khi s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5393","checkdouble":"194322"},{"date":"17:27 12/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 12/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/18/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-1208.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 12/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 1208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-1208-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real nh\u1eafm Eriksen thay Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid mua Christian Eriksen trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Luka Modric t\u1edbi Inter Milan, theo The Sun Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 mua Eden Hazard, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Daily v\u00e0 Sunday Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Inter th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Luciano Spalletti kh\u00f4ng tin Inter Milan c\u00f3 Luka Modric. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Inter c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Modric mu\u1ed1n anh t\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" title=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Alvaro-Morata-phat-bieu-ve-Mateo-Kovacic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Modric khuy\u00ean Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u1edf Stamford Bridge ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e0n anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Luka Modric c\u0169ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 anh th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi-180-194183.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/17/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-dam-phan-mua-mauro-icardi-180-194183.html\">B\u1ecb nh\u0103m nhe c\u01b0\u1edbp Modric, Real ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n Inter</span><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Mauro Icardi. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric b\u1ecb Inter Milan ve v\u00e3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Marcelo cho Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo cho Juventus. Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Real quan t\u00e2m Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Martial\" title=\"tien dao Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Marca, Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real t\u00ednh mua Thiago thay Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Navas tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Navas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Courtois, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5392","checkdouble":"194328"},{"date":"17:04 12/08","title":"\"Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/arsenal-co-the-nam-trong-nhom-xuong-hang-sau-2-vong-dau-dau-tien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Merson lo s\u1ee3 Arsenal tr\u1eafng tay sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Arsenal, ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Man City. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/arsenal-co-the-nam-trong-nhom-xuong-hang-sau-2-vong-dau-dau-tien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Merson lo ng\u1ea1i Arsenal s\u1ebd t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Chelsea, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 \u1edf Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Merson ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cUnai Emery c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Man City sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cEmery m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i lo s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Paul Merson ca ng\u1ee3i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Emery</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Arsenal, song Paul Merson \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/emery-quyet-tam-chan-dung-mach-thua-truoc-guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Paul Merson ca ng\u1ee3i HLV Unai Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEmery \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Stephan Lichtsteiner, Lucas Torreira, Bern Leno v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u1ea7n. Arsenal c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, Sokratis v\u00e0 Lichtsteiner l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung h\u1ee3p l\u00fd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 34 hay 35 nh\u01b0 Lichtsteiner ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Arsenal. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Lichtsteiner s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-man-city-22h-ngay-128-khac-biet-o-nen-tang-172-194293.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Man City</span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5391","checkdouble":"194321"},{"date":"16:38 12/08","title":"Gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/giu-sach-luoi-thu-mon-71-trieu-bang-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Chelsea, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKepa g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khung g\u1ed7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp The Blues \u0111\u1ebfn khi ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng trong 90 ph\u00fat, gi\u00fap Chelsea th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n, trung v\u1ec7 Antonio Rudiger cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Kepa \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield\" title=\"Kepa vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/giu-sach-luoi-thu-mon-71-trieu-bang-duoc-dong-doi-ca-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Chelsea hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac Thibaut g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Kepa &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi &ndash; nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp thu chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t&rdquo; &ndash; Rudiger k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1, vi\u1ec7c Kepa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn anh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-thang-hoanh-trang-chua-the-mung-voi-nhung-diem-yeu-chet-nguoi-172-194288.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/chelsea-thang-hoanh-trang-chua-the-mung-voi-nhung-diem-yeu-chet-nguoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-thang-hoanh-trang-chua-the-mung-voi-nhung-diem-yeu-chet-nguoi-172-194288.html\">Chelsea th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng: Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 m\u1eebng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nTrong ni\u1ec1m h\u00e2n hoan gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Chelsea b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea-172-194286.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield-172-194299.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-chi-ra-2-diem-yeu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-huddersfield-172-194299.html\">Sarri ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Huddersfield</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri v\u1eeba ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Chelsea c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Huddersfield.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5390","checkdouble":"194323"},{"date":"17:03 12/08","title":"V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EPL, Jurgen Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong th\u00e1nh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/vo-dich-epl-jurgen-klopp-se-duoc-phong-thanh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Rush chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi 4 t\u00e2n binh \u0111em v\u1ec1 trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho Jurgen Klopp, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, Ian Rush cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i Premier League. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Steve McManaman, Robbie Fowler, Steven Gerrard, Jamie Carragher, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o n\u0103m nay, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i, c\u00f2n HLV Jurgen Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong th\u00e1nh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ian Rush chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool: Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong th\u00e1nh n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/klopp-thua-nhan-liverpool-chot-so-chuyen-nhuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ian Rush chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool: Klopp s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong th\u00e1nh n\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00e3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Kenny v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1990. V\u00e0o l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ai cho r\u1eb1ng 30 n\u0103m t\u1edbi Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 18 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, khi \u0111\u00f3 M.U m\u1edbi c\u00f3 7. Gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch 20 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng im t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Klopp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau qu\u00fd. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eb1ng sau \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Trong 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Van Dijk v\u00e0 Alisson &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a CLB&rdquo; &ndash; Ian Rush chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu-172-194284.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu-172-194284.html\">Bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Liverpool xo\u00e1y s\u00e2u v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a MU</span><br>\r\nFabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc-172-194241.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc-172-194241.html\">Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nG\u1ea7n 3 th\u00e1ng sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, n\u1ed7i \u0111au v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i ngoai v\u1edbi Liverpool. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Klopp ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Ramos v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eadt v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang-172-193863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang-172-193863.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Premier League 2018/19: \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 ngai v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m, g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00f4i qua, c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1eabn m\u1ecfi m\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5389","checkdouble":"194324"},{"date":"17:42 12/08","title":"Pogba: \"C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-co-hay-khong-bang-doi-truong-toi-van-la-thu-linh-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0n\u201d \u1edf Old Trafford b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Man Utd \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 m\u1edf ra th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-co-hay-khong-bang-doi-truong-toi-van-la-thu-linh-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, vinh d\u1ef1 n\u00e0y cho Pogba c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 th\u00e2m ni\u00ean h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Antonio Valencia, Ashley Young hay Chris Smalling. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c \u1edf Old Trafford v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y: \u201cKhi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 cho Man Utd l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u, Rio Ferdinand v\u00e0 Patrice Evra l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng. L\u00fac gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Gianluigi Buffon v\u00e0 Giorgio Chiellini. T\u00f4i h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1eeb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n n\u00f3 th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn ch\u1ee9c danh \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0m cho t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n y\u00eau MU v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111eo b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean tay, nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c v\u1eady sau t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh \u1edf n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i c\u00e0ng \u00fd th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch l\u1edbn lao n\u00e0y khi hay bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a CLB, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec h\u1ecd.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Video MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5388","checkdouble":"194325"},{"date":"17:24 12/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Arsenal vs Man City 22h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/arsenal-vs-man-city-ngoai-hang-anh-1282018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { disp